Symbol.Script_3D:
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then END
if not(gs_shadow) then SHADOW OFF
pen gs_cont_pen
! --- Vertical Frame ----------------------------------------------------------- dist_fr=(a - (num_fr * frw)) / (num_fr - 1)
MATERIAL frmat for k2 = 1 to 2 for k1 = 0 to num_fr-1 block frw, frw, zzyzx-sht addx dist_fr + frw next k1 del (num_fr) addy (b-frw) next k2 del 2
! --- Frame Members ------------------------------------------------------------
MATERIAL fmmat zdist_sh =(zzyzx - bshelf_h)/ (num_sh-1) !distance between shelves for k4 = 0 to num_sh-1 addz bshelf_h-fmw-sht for k3 = 0 to num_fr-1 addy frw block frw, b-(2*frw), fmw !y direction del 1 addx dist_fr+frw next k3 del (num_fr) del 1
addz bshelf_h-fmw-sht for k6 = 1 to 2 for k5 = 0 to num_fr-2 addx frw block dist_fr, frw, fmw !x direction del 1 addx dist_fr+frw next k5 del (num_fr-1) addy (b-frw) next k6 del 2 del 1 addz zdist_sh next k4 del (num_sh)
! --- Shelves ------------------------------------------------------------
MATERIAL shmat
!Top shelf
addz zzyzx-sht if benchtype_m = 0 then block a, b, sht gosub 2000 else ntop=(b)/frw num_btop=INT(ntop/2) dtop=((b)-(num_btop+1)*frw)/(num_btop)
for k10=0 to (num_btop) block a,frw,sht !x direction gosub 2000 addy dtop+frw next k10 del (num_btop) del 1 endif del 1
!Shelves
for k7 = 1 to (num_sh-1) addz bshelf_h-sht if benchtype_m = 0 then !flat if num_fr>2 then gosub "flatshelf1" else gosub "flatshelf2" endif gosub 2000 else !slatted n = (b-2*frw)/frw num_b = INT(n/2) d = ((b-2*frw)-num_b*frw)/(num_b+1)
gosub "slattedside" gosub "slattedmiddle" endif del 1 addz zdist_sh next k7 del (num_sh-1)
END
"flatshelf1": for n=1 to (num_fr-2) PUT n*(dist_fr+frw), 0, 15 PUT n*(dist_fr+frw), frw, 15 PUT n*(dist_fr+frw)+frw,frw, 15 PUT n*(dist_fr+frw)+frw,0, 15 next n
for n=1 to (num_fr-2) PUT a-n*(dist_fr+frw), b, 15 PUT a-n*(dist_fr+frw), b-frw, 15 PUT a-(n*(dist_fr+frw)+frw),b-frw, 15 PUT a-(n*(dist_fr+frw)+frw),b, 15 next n
prism_ 13+2*(num_fr-2)*4,sht, 0, frw, 15, frw, frw, 15, frw, 0, 15, GET (NSP/2), a-frw, 0, 15, a-frw, frw, 15, a, frw, 15, a, b-frw, 15, a-frw, b-frw, 15, a-frw, b, 15, GET (NSP), frw, b, 15, frw, b-frw, 15, 0, b-frw, 15, 0, frw, -1
return
"flatshelf2": prism_ 13, sht, 0, frw, 15, frw, frw, 15, frw, 0, 15, a-frw, 0, 15, a-frw, frw, 15, a, frw, 15, a, b-frw, 15, a-frw, b-frw, 15, a-frw, b, 15, frw, b, 15, frw, b-frw, 15, 0, b-frw, 15, 0, frw, -1 return
"slattedside": for side=1 to 2 for polc=0 to num_fr-2 addx frw block dist_fr, frw, sht !!x direction gosub 2000 del 1 addx dist_fr+frw next polc del (num_fr-1) addy (b-frw) next side del 2 return
"slattedmiddle": for mid=1 to num_b addy frw+d block a,frw,sht !!x direction gosub 2000 del 1 addy frw+d next mid del num_b return
2000: vert 0, 0, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 0, 0, 1 coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4 base body -1 return
Symbol.Script_2D:
pen gs_cont_pen rect2 0,0,a,b
fill gs_fill_type poly2_b 5,7, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0,1, 0,b,1, a,b,1, a,0,1, 0,0,-1 unId = 1 HOTSPOT2 0,b, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 a/2,b/2, unID : unID = unID + 1
CALL "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" Parameters ALL
dist_fr=(a-(num_fr*frw))/(num_fr-1)
unID = 10 for k=1 to (num_fr-2) add2 frw+dist_fr+frw/2,0 LINE2 0,0,0,b HOTSPOT2 0,0, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 0,b, unID : unID = unID + 1 del 1 add2 dist_fr+frw,0 next k del (num_fr-2)
call "fa_minimalspace" parameters all MSType = 1, unID = 3000
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "b_typ" stBenchTypes values "benchtype_m" 0, 1
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "b_typ" then if b_typ = stBenchTypes[1] then benchtype_m = 0 !flat if b_typ = stBenchTypes[2] then benchtype_m = 1 !slatted parameters benchtype_m = benchtype_m else if benchtype_m = 0 then b_typ = stBenchTypes[1] if benchtype_m = 1 then b_typ = stBenchTypes[2] parameters b_typ = b_typ endif
values "gs_detlevel_3D" stDetail3D values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 0, 1
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then if gs_detlevel_3D = stDetail3D[1] then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 !off if gs_detlevel_3D = stDetail3D[2] then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 !detailed parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m else if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then gs_detlevel_3D = stDetail3D[1] if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then gs_detlevel_3D = stDetail3D[2] parameters gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D endif
IF gs_cont_pen=0 then PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=7 IF gs_fill_pen=0 then PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=91
values "frw" range [0.01,) values "fmw" range [0.01,) values "sht" range [0.01,) values "b" range [5*frw,) values "num_fr" range [2,) values "num_sh" range [2,) values "num_fr" range [2,) values "num_sh" range [2,) values "bshelf_h" range [fmw + sht,)
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then HIDEPARAMETER "gs_shadow"
! Minimal Space
values "MSFront" range [0,)
Symbol.Script_1D:
DIM stBenchTypes[2] stBenchTypes[1] = `Flat Bench` stBenchTypes[2] = `Slatted Bench`
DIM stDetail3D[2] stDetail3D[1] = `Off` stDetail3D[2] = `Detailed`
Symbol.Comment: Expandable book shelves mounted on frame with optional shelf styles and minimal space.
